## Graph Change Events

Subscribe to real-time graph changes via EventEmitter:

```typescript
storage.events.on('entityCreated', (event) => {
  console.log(`Created: ${event.entity.name} at ${event.timestamp}`);
});

storage.events.on('entityUpdated', (event) => {
  console.log(`Updated: ${event.entity.name}`, event.changes);
});

storage.events.on('graphSaved', (event) => {
  console.log(`Saved ${event.entityCount} entities`);
});
```

Available events:
- `entityCreated`, `entityUpdated`, `entityDeleted`
- `relationCreated`, `relationDeleted`
- `observationAdded`, `observationDeleted`
- `graphLoaded`, `graphSaved`
